707502f.title: Manhattan: 1st Ave. - 4th St. E.
707502f.text:
First Ave., west side, north from East 4th., to, but not including
East 5th Streets. The Second Ave., Elevated is shown on First Ave.
About 1910.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.

707503f-a.title: Manhattan: 1st Ave. - 4th St.
707503f-a.text:
68-76 First Avenue, east side, between 4th and 5th Streets.
June 25, 1934.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
